QUERY_TEXT:
select "position budget org hierarchy"."level_8" as "level_8"
from "und"."staff_job_change_event_fact" "staff job change event fact"
  inner join "und"."organization_hierarchy" "position budget org hierarchy" on ("staff job change event fact"."position_budget_org_key" = "position budget org hierarchy"."organization_hierarchy_key")
  inner join "und"."date" "date" on ("staff job change event fact"."job_change_event_date_key" = "date"."date_key")
where (("date"."full_date" >= '1985-01-01 00:00:00.000'::timestamp_ntz) and ("staff job change event fact"."staff_job_change_event" <> 'separation'))
group by 1
order by 1 asc
Inner Join: join "und"."organization_hierarchy" "position budget org hierarchy" on ("staff job change event fact"."position_budget_org_key" = "position budget org hierarchy"."organization_hierarchy_key")

Inner Join: join information_schema.columns c on c.table_name = 'nsf_r_d_expenditure_fact' and c.table_schema = 'dbo' and sc.columnname = c.column_name where

QUERY_TEXT: select lower(columnrestriction), columnname from dw_security.columnrestriction sc inner join information_schema.columns c on c.table_name = 'ipeds_degree_completions_attribute' and c.table_schema = 'dbo' and sc.columnname = c.column_name  where tableid = 79 and lower(columnrestriction) = 'r' and c.data_type = 'text' and c.character_maximum_length = '4' and columnname <> 'ipeds_degree_completions_attribute_key' order by ordinal_position asc;
Inner Join: join information_schema.columns c on c.table_name = 'ipeds_degree_completions_attribute' and c.table_schema = 'dbo' and sc.columnname = c.column_name  where
